pageContext.claim: “When you hear the Fake News talking negatively about my meeting with President Putin, and all that I gave up, remember, I gave up NOTHING, we merely talked about future benefits for both countries. Also, we got along very well, which is a good thing, except for the Corrupt Media!”
pageContext.analysis: Since Trump met alone with Putin and no detailed readout has been given, it is uncertain whether Trump gave up anything. However, simply be meeting with Putin despite U.S. sanctions and no change in Russian behavior, Trump offered the Russian president significant diplomatic benefits.
